&lt;h2 id="how-to-transplant-efficiently">How to transplant efficiently&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="prepare-no-dig-beds">Prepare No Dig beds&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>The No Dig approach is a way to make market gardening successful because it works similarly to how nature works.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>It is about:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>not digging or tilling the soil&lt;/li>
&lt;li>keeping the soil covered at all times with organic matter&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Why is it an efficient approach?&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>It feeds the soil web&lt;/li>
&lt;li>It keeps the weeds away&lt;/li>
&lt;li>It makes it very easy to transplant.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
