&lt;h3 id="transplanting-from-500httpsyoutube1jgwrfenqy0t300">Transplanting (&lt;a href="https://youtu.be/1JgWrFENqy0?t=300">from 5:00&lt;/a>)&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Once the beds are ready, you will need to loosen up the individual transplant without damaging them.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>
&lt;img src="https://iamjeremie.me/post/2023-04/market-gardening-in-april-the-dutch-farmer/images/loosing-up-the-transplants-with-a-dibble-plate.jpg"
